<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国 - 南华早报</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/rss/4/feed</link><description>来自中国的最新突发新闻。</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 23:25:14 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>随着加密货币价格飙升克服了政府禁令的耻辱，比特币仍然是中国社交媒体上的快速热门话题</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3253562/bitcoin-remains-fast-trending-topic-chinese-social-media-cryptocurrencys-surging-price-overcomes?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>人们对比特币的兴趣日益浓厚，反映出尽管政府出台了全面禁令，但中国大陆的加密货币爱好者社区仍在蓬勃发展。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 23:00:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3253562/bitcoin-remains-fast-trending-topic-chinese-social-media-cryptocurrencys-surging-price-overcomes?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国总理在北京会见美国商业团体作为魅力攻势的一部分</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253583/chinese-premier-meets-us-business-group-beijing-part-charm-offensive?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>李强对美国商会主席率领的代表团表示，华盛顿对华贸易的“小院子、高围栏”做法不符合双方利益。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:24:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253583/chinese-premier-meets-us-business-group-beijing-part-charm-offensive?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国前总领事表示，即将出台的香港国安法引发了“越来越多的担忧”</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3253582/impending-hong-kong-security-law-language-stirs-growing-concern-former-us-consul-general-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>汉斯科姆·史密斯引用了政府咨询文件，表明可能会针对在该市运营的实体与海外实体之间的联系进行攻击。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 20:16:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3253582/impending-hong-kong-security-law-language-stirs-growing-concern-former-us-consul-general-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>欧盟未能通过要求对中国供应商进行人权和环境审计的法律</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253564/eu-fails-pass-supply-chain-law-would-have-required-firms-carry-out-human-rights-and-environmental?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>这些规则没有直接点名中国，但欧盟主要公司将被要求对外国商业伙伴进行详细审计。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:00:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253564/eu-fails-pass-supply-chain-law-would-have-required-firms-carry-out-human-rights-and-environmental?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国领导结束乌克兰与俄罗斯战争的谈判的时机可能很快就会成熟</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252998/time-could-soon-be-ripe-china-lead-negotiations-end-ukraine-russia-war?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>经过两年的战争，中国未能帮助乌克兰实现和平。但这种情况可能即将改变。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3252998/time-could-soon-be-ripe-china-lead-negotiations-end-ukraine-russia-war?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车厂商对苹果取消汽车项目的决定感到惊讶，小米首席执行官雷军表示他仍然致力于</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253542/chinese-ev-players-surprised-apples-decision-cancel-car-project-xiaomi-ceo-lei-saying-he-remains?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>从小米到小鹏汽车，中国电动汽车制造商的领导人都表示不相信苹果会结束其长达十年的汽车制造努力。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:30:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/big-tech/article/3253542/chinese-ev-players-surprised-apples-decision-cancel-car-project-xiaomi-ceo-lei-saying-he-remains?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>北京警方暗示“两会”时间加强安保</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253536/beijing-police-give-hint-about-two-sessions-timing-security-stepped?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>禁止包括无人机在内的低空飞机的通知表明，政治会议可能会在 3 月 12 日之前结束。对入境包裹和进入中国首都的火车乘客也进行了额外检查。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:00:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253536/beijing-police-give-hint-about-two-sessions-timing-security-stepped?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>前官员称，在与美国的“金融战”中，中国可能面临资本难题</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253532/finance-war-us-former-official-says-china-risks-staring-down-barrel-capital-conundrum?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>备受瞩目的经济学家、前国务院研究员警告称，美联储降息后，美国可能向中国注资，可能会给已经遭受重创的市场带来动荡。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:00:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253532/finance-war-us-former-official-says-china-risks-staring-down-barrel-capital-conundrum?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>高级官员表示，中国修订的国家秘密法的成功取决于广泛的宣传和教育</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253534/success-chinas-revised-state-secrets-law-depends-widespread-publicity-and-education-says-senior?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>国家保密局局长写道，公众必须了解修订后的保守国家秘密法规定的义务。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 12:00:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/politics/article/3253534/success-chinas-revised-state-secrets-law-depends-widespread-publicity-and-education-says-senior?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>顾问表示，中国中央政府应在刺激消费方面发挥主导作用</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253533/chinas-central-government-should-take-leading-role-kick-starting-consumption-adviser-says?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>一位中国经济顾问表示，中央政府应该利用其相对较低的债务比率，利用其资源来刺激消费和引导有效投资——这是中国试图回归稳定增长模式时迫切需要的两件事。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 12:00:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/economy/china-economy/article/3253533/chinas-central-government-should-take-leading-role-kick-starting-consumption-adviser-says?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国驻联合国特使警告以色列-加沙战争升级可能蔓延至叙利亚，加剧人道主义危机</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253550/chinas-un-envoy-warns-escalated-israel-gaza-war-could-spillover-syria-worsen-humanitarian-crisis?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>在安理会通报会上，戴兵敦促以色列开放加沙地带的人道主义通道，限制对叙利亚目标的空袭。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:25:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253550/chinas-un-envoy-warns-escalated-israel-gaza-war-could-spillover-syria-worsen-humanitarian-crisis?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>中国乌克兰和平特使将第二次访问欧洲和俄罗斯促谈</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253546/chinas-ukraine-peace-envoy-make-second-visit-europe-and-russia-promote-talks?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>李辉去年首次访华是为了推动北京方面的谈判解决计划，但后来承认没有立即取得进展</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:09:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/3253546/chinas-ukraine-peace-envoy-make-second-visit-europe-and-russia-promote-talks?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>报告发现，由于供不应求，中国以高额薪资吸引人工智能人才</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3253492/china-lures-ai-talent-hefty-salary-premium-demand-far-exceeds-supply-report-finds?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>随着中国一些顶尖人才流向美国，中国的雇主正在争夺具有生成人工智能技能的员工。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:30:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/tech/tech-trends/article/3253492/china-lures-ai-talent-hefty-salary-premium-demand-far-exceeds-supply-report-finds?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>美国发布行政命令，确保美国人的敏感个人数据免受“关注国家”的侵害</title><link>https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3253438/us-issues-executive-order-keep-americans-sensitive-personal-data-safe-countries-concern?utm_source=rss_feed</link><description>前所未有的指令重点关注解决外国对手获取访问权限的合法手段，例如通过数据经纪人获取信息。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:00:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.scmp.com/news/china/article/3253438/us-issues-executive-order-keep-americans-sensitive-personal-data-safe-countries-concern?utm_source=rss_feed</guid></item><item><title>随着新航